# Garlic Butter Prawns

## Ingredients

* 500-600 g prawns
* 50-100 g butter
* 5-10 garlic cloves minced
* 1 Tb cooking wine

## Extras

* 1 tsp fish sauce
* sugar to sweeten
* cornstarch to thicken sauce
* veggies

## Method


## Notes
